field_mapping_query.sql:
SELECT
id as _id,
type,
i.repo.id as repo_id,
i.actor.id as actr_id,
i.org.id as org_id,
CASE
WHEN i.payload.comment is not null
THEN ARRAY_EXCEPT(TOKENIZE(i.payload.comment.body),
ARRAY_CREATE('a','b','c','d','e','f','g','h','i','j','k','l','m','n','o','p',
'q','r','s','t','u','v','w','x','y','z','1','2','3','4','5','6','7','8','9','0')
)
ELSE null
END as comment_body_tokenized,
* EXCEPT(id, repo, actor, org, _meta)
FROM _input i
CLUSTER BY type

field_mapping_query.sql:
SELECT
CAST(_input.Product.ProductID as string) as _id,
_input.Product.Details.Name as ProductName,
_input.Product.Details.ProductCategory as ProductCategory,
_input.Product.Details.Description as ProductDescription,
_input.Product.Details.Price as Price,
ARRAY_DISTINCT(ARRAY_CONCAT(
TOKENIZE(_input.Product.Details.Name),
PREFIXES(lower(_input.Product.Details.Name), 4),
ARRAY_MAP('trim', NGRAMS(lower(_input.Product.Details.Name), 2)),
ARRAY_MAP('trim', NGRAMS(lower(_input.Product.Details.Name), 3))
)) as NameSearchArray,
ARRAY_DISTINCT(ARRAY_CONCAT(
TOKENIZE(_input.Product.Details.Description),
PREFIXES(lower(_input.Product.Details.Description), 4),
ARRAY_MAP('trim', NGRAMS(lower(_input.Product.Details.Description), 2)),
ARRAY_MAP('trim', NGRAMS(lower(_input.Product.Details.Description), 3))
)) as DescriptionSearchArray,
ARRAY_DISTINCT(ARRAY_CONCAT(
TOKENIZE(_input.Product.Details.ProductCategory),
PREFIXES(lower(_input.Product.Details.ProductCategory), 4),
ARRAY_MAP('trim', NGRAMS(lower(_input.Product.Details.ProductCategory), 2)),
ARRAY_MAP('trim', NGRAMS(lower(_input.Product.Details.ProductCategory), 3))
)) as CategorySearchArray,
_meta
FROM
_input

field_mapping_query.sql:
WITH real_time_pickups AS (
SELECT
trip_id as _id,
i.taxi_id,
i.company AS company,
PARSE_TIMESTAMP('%m/%d/%Y %I:%M:%S %p', i.start_ts, 'America/Chicago') as pickup_ts,
i.pickup_area,
ST_GEOGFROMTEXT(i.pickup_geo) as pickup_geo,
i.pickup_lat,
i.pickup_lon
FROM
_input i
WHERE
i.start_ts IS NOT NULL
)
SELECT
rtp.taxi_id,
rtp.company,
rtp.pickup_ts,
rtp.pickup_area,
rtp.pickup_geo,
rtp.pickup_lat,
rtp.pickup_lon
FROM
real_time_pickups rtp
